title: SPACIOUS & OPEN AREA DESIGN FLOOR~3 BED/2 BATH HOME FOR RENT#
posting_body: ['****', 'Easy access to I-90 & I-405 and access to parks & trails****', 'SPACIOUS & OPEN AREA DESIGN FLOOR~3 BED/2 BATH HOME FOR RENT#', 'Gorgeous rambler in the fantastic neighborhood of Spiritridge.', 'Spacious & open area design floor plan w/ gleaming hardwood floors, formal living room, family room & large dining room.', 'Slate & butcher block counters, Stainless steel appliances, bright skylights, master bdr w/ huge walk in closet, 5 piece master bath with jetted tub.', 'This home has it all, flat & fenced backyard enjoys sunny western exposure.', 'Fantastic Bellevue Schools.', 'Easy access to I-90 & I-405 and access to parks & trails.']
